But I didn't want to let others know about the gem well I explored.

55
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,360
 So under the cover of night, 

56
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:30,180
 I went to conceal it. 

57
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,840
 But without vitality, 

58
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:39,020
