 Right at that time... 

60
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:29,520
Didn't you say it was a companion who died of illness?

61
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,380
Grandpa, which of your words is true?

62
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:37,720
