A different person?

118
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,660
How will you change?

119
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,940
Well...

120
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,512
Same appearance...

121
00:09:33,512 --> 00:09:39,260
But the character and behaviors are totally different.

122
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,980
Mu Dai.

123
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,940
Have you ever heard a saying?

124
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:57,820
Human body cells undergo constant metabolism.

125
00:09:57,820 --> 00:10:02,840
It takes seven years for your body to change all its cells.

126
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:07,200
So in seven years, we will both become brand-new.

127
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,120
We will both change.

128
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,360
Will we?

129
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,380
When I came back from Heisha,

130
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,820
Ping Ting said to me,

131
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:29,860
"Brother Ren, you seem to be a different person."

132
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:35,320
But I think those who really care about you

133
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:39,420
