136
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:55,100
So you'll recognize me, right?

137
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:57,720
Yes.

138
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:05,660
Remember your words.

139
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:07,280
It's a deal.

140
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:09,020
Words count.

141
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,520
Deal.

