157
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,520
Very possibly.

158
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:20,240
Deep in the mountains, the rain, the village, and the Sunny Doll.

159
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,960
Every one of them is here.

160
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,760
And not only was this savage strong,

161
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:28,940
but she also faked signs along the way, using the Sunny Doll to confuse us.

162
00:12:28,940 --> 00:12:32,240
Such intelligence is suspicious.

163
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:36,320
The clam was hard to deal with.

164
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,860
This time, what we'll face is a live person.

165
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:39,360
We...

166
